African Development Week&nbsp;opens in Dakar, Senegal. Hosted by the Economic Commission for Africa (ECA) and the African Union, the 2nd African Development Week, from March 23-28, is also the stage for the annual high-level joint ECA-AU ministerial Conference, which brings together AU Ministers of the Economy and Finance and the ECA Ministers of Finance, Planning and Economic Development. More on the African Development Week and the ECA in this BRIEFING.&nbsp;